**Project Name:** DOM Manipulation Part Two

**Description:**  
This project uses JavaScript DOM manipulation to build an interactive 
navigation menu and submenu. It practices selecting elements, styling 
them, handling click events, and using event delegation.

**Built With:**  
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

**Features:**  
- Dynamic top menu links
- Submenu styling with JavaScript
- Click event handling
- Event delegation
- `preventDefault()` for links



